{"tid":1252963,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳健民: \"不受傷、不被捕，是指領䄂......\"","createTime":"2019-06-23T10:01:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T10:06:25.000Z","uid":131171,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f5ca0f2327c0a071e16f92bdf7ec74991e2defce","tid":1252963,"uid":131171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T10:01:39.000Z","msg":"【不受傷、不被捕，是指領䄂？】<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/15kUYu2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F15kUYu2.png&h=6c588140&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n你哋做就係神，人哋做就係鬼。嗱，我讀得書少，你唔好呃我。阿鄺俊宇佔中糾察；而家，究竟係，要自首，定係，不被捕？究竟勸人「不受傷、不被捕」，係「讓領導先走、無政治道德人格」，定係「保護羣眾」？<br />\n<br />\n你知道朱凱迪提出的「每周末舉行社會運動&sup1;」是從那裏來的嗎？是戴耀廷看到黃背心後提出的「在星期六、日才出來做抗爭&sup2;」。「愛與和平可穿透坦克」、「温柔是最大的武器」，相隔一段時間，轉一些事換一些人&sup3;，同一套戲就可以拍續集；不斷輪迴，不斷犯同一樣的錯誤。<br />\n<br />\n香港不是太政治化，而是政治太宗教化。你們這些假冒為善的人有禍了，拜偶像的人也當得禍。捧偶像、默站、遊行、捐款、唱歌，然後解散等下次集會；拜神、默禱、苦行、奉獻、詩歌、然後阿門等下一次彌撒。用宗教思維搞民運，你最終就只能殉道，除了ISIS。種瓜得瓜，因果不仁；對人不對事，你就會得到人治。<br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n<br />\n「對抗一個極權政府，用殉道主義搞民運，是求死。選擇跟從這種民運方式，是跟住去死。參與民運不是為進入天國，請把教條留在教會。香港人不是未有條件民主，而是未有準備過真的要民運，從來就如選舉般只得囗號。香港人未有的，是民運所必需要有的反抗精神。」<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2LC7ZRc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2LC7ZRc&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaOQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=7276a43e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2LC7ZRc</a><br />\n<br />\n&sup1; <a href=\"http://bit.ly/31O8Shh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F31O8Shh&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaOQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=de8291f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/31O8Shh</a><br />\n&sup2; <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2KyVwjt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KyVwjt&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaOQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=9669aa23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2KyVwjt</a><br />\n&sup3; <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2N3ZsuS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2N3ZsuS&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaOQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=542ebbc1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2N3ZsuS</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/politicmood/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpoliticmood%2F&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaOQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=3244bacc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/politicmood/</a>"},{"pid":"f4ba11080aa8493a5638b3c4418fe1551fca6270","tid":1252963,"uid":131171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T10:02:01.000Z","msg":"黃洋達：【「不受傷，不被捕」這綱領的真正意思】<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1252923\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1252923</a>"},{"pid":"bcbf18109b1fda70cb6bc96c96100b04252f36dd","tid":1252963,"uid":121546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T10:04:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日野餐係口罩上面寫+852 抗議黑警冇number</span></span>"},{"pid":"31fa700169e91083f91505a9e674355c18e68712","tid":1252963,"uid":80303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T10:05:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好講舊事喇</span>"},{"pid":"9ec594eaf18050cc2b08f9a458bb0d83fd601c14","tid":1252963,"uid":121546,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T10:05:42.000Z","msg":"食屎啦，聲譽同議席就你拎，仲要市民代你比人拉"},{"pid":"a003b34a7f88c763f6b6a13fd2acf7cef3ac4af4","tid":1252963,"uid":1372,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T10:06:25.000Z","msg":"熱狗page<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}